rows.label: qst103608_msg0002
rows.name: The ship... has it already departed?

rows.label: qst103608_msg0003
rows.name: Yes... We let Senator Stol escape.

rows.label: qst103608_msg0004
rows.name:
His comrades were hiding
inside the ship.

rows.label: qst103608_msg0005
rows.name:
The attack by Brionac was
a diversion to allow Senator
Stol to escape...

rows.label: qst103608_msg0009
rows.name:
I will chase him to the
ends of the earth.

rows.label: qst103608_msg0010
rows.name:
I will report this
matter to my superiors!
